      "role": "user",
      "content": "the goblin metaphors are a bit distracting, can we stick to the technical side? specifically, if i can't use valgrind because this is a bare-metal environment with no OS, what are my actual options for tracking down these rogue allocations?",
      "source": "evaluator"
